  static const String texte =
      'Our planet Earth has been called the Blue Planet since the days of space travel, because the water covering almost 3/4 of its surface shines blue when seen from space. It is this water that sustains life on Earth. Because of its importance, ancient Greek philosophers considered it one of the four primordial elements. In Hindu culture, it is seen as a symbol of life and purity.Water has many facets in the life of mankind: it can be both friend and foe. Humanity uses water for many purposes. But it is also a destructive force, as we see in the natural disasters, floods and tsunamis that continue to occur regularly today.So man’s relationship with water is twofold: to use the opportunities it offers and to protect against the threats it poses. The technical tasks involved are mainly solved by civil and mechanical engineers using engineering tools and methods. These professionals work in close cooperation: buildings are needed to house mechanical equipment, and machinery is needed to operate water systems.';
